Building TV
===========

1. Install the following packages (Fedora):
	a. gdm-devel
	b. gcc
	c. make
	d. git
	e. gcc-c++
	f. java-1.8.0-openjdk	
	g. swig
	h. gpm-static
	i. gpm-devel
2. Install maven and add it to PATH
3. export PERLLIB=/path/to/source/turbovision
4. export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.162-3.b12.fc28.x86_64
4. cd library && ./configure && make

Building the SWIG module
========================
2. cd swig && ./compile.sh -sdm

Running the demo
================
1. cd swig
2. ./runme.sh
